<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Statistika - Drugi Kolokvij (Uskoro)</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #3b82f6;
            --secondary-color: #2563eb;
            --background-color: #E8E8E8;
            --text-color: #1e293b;
            --card-background: #ffffff;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: var(--card-background);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .coming-soon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .notify-button {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .notify-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .notify-button:focus {
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px;
                width: 90%;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            .coming-soon {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .logo-link:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .logo-image {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .logo-image {
                width: 50px;
                height: 50px;
            }
            .company-name {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <a href="/" class="logo-link">
                <img src="/sprites/logo.ico" alt="Stat&Mat Logo" class="logo-image">
                <span class="company-name">Stat&Mat</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <h1>Statistika - Drugi Kolokvij</h1>
        
        <p class="coming-soon">Uskoro dolazi!</p>
        
        <p>
            Pripremamo sveobuhvatni materijal za učenje koji će vam pomoći u savladavanju gradiva 
            i pripremi za drugi kolokvij iz statistike. Ostanite s nama!
        </p>
        
        <h2>Što možete očekivati?</h2>
        <p>
            Detaljne video lekcije, primjere zadataka, i interaktivne vježbe koje će vam pomoći 
            da s lakoćom savladate gradivo drugog kolokvija iz statistike.
        </p>
        <p>
            Budite među prvima koji će saznati kada sadržaj bude dostupan. 
            Prijavite se za obavijesti i osigurajte si prednost u učenju!
        </p>

        <button type="submit" class="notify-button">OBAVIJESTI ME</button>

    </div>
</body>
</html>

